      "content": "hey so im 20 weeks pregnant and i have this really bad sinus infection that just wont go away mcm sinuse are killing me... i was gonna take some sudafed but i wasnt sure if that was okay? also i have some ciprofloxacin left over from a few months ago do u think that would work for a sinus thing?",
